    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, showroom-quality shine, and the interior is pristine with no signs of wear on the leather or trim. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history. A rare find for a buyer seeking a car in truly impeccable, investment-grade condition.",
      "price": 49000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly pristine condition. This motorcar has been curated with an uncompromising commitment to maintenance, resulting in a showroom-quality aesthetic that is indistinguishable from new. Every surface, from the lustrous exterior finish to the meticulously preserved interior, reflects a life of climate-controlled storage and expert care. This is a definitive example for the discerning collector who accepts only the finest. Experience the unrivaled performance and prestige of a vehicle that sets the standard for its class.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! Thanks for taking a look at my pride and joy. I\u2019ve spent more time polishing this beauty than I care to admit, and it really shows\u2014she\u2019s in truly spectacular, showroom-level shape. I've kept her tucked away in a heated garage and only took her out on the clearest blue-sky days. Aside from maybe a tiny, barely-there speck from a Sunday drive, she is absolutely flawless and drives like she just left the factory. It breaks my heart a little to let her go, but I\u2019d love to see her go to someone who appreciates a perfect ride as much as I do. Come by, let's grab a coffee, and I'll show you why this is the one you've been waiting for!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanical masterpiece: this E92 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, presented in absolute collector-grade condition. The S65 V8 delivers a linear power band to its 8,400 RPM redline with surgical precision, having undergone a proactive rod bearing service and throttle actuator refresh to ensure zero-latency response. The chassis is exceptionally taut, benefiting from a reinforced subframe that eliminates factory compliance, while the 6-speed manual provides a bolt-action shift feel. Every component, from the limited-slip differential to the EDC suspension, operates within tight factory tolerances. Finished in Alpine White with exceptional paint depth, this vehicle has been curated for the purist who demands peak mechanical harmony and a visceral driving experience. No deferred maintenance, just pure, high-strung performance.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Flawless condition. Zero issues. Showroom quality at a steal. Act now or miss out.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a world where time stands still. This isn't just a vehicle; it\u2019s a symphony of hand-stitched leather and polished chrome that whispers of moonlit drives and coastal escapes. Every curve of its silhouette captures the golden hour light, reflecting a life lived with exquisite taste. It carries the quiet confidence of a masterpiece preserved in a silk-lined vault, ready to transport you not just to your destination, but to an era of pure, unadulterated class. To drive it is to command the road with a grace that modern machines have long forgotten. Own a piece of history that remains as vibrant and breathtaking as the day it first turned heads.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle arrives in absolute showroom condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards since its inception. With its flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new, it offers a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection. Fully inspected and certified by our master technicians, this vehicle represents the benchmark for its class and is ready for immediate delivery.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to be listing my pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for this absolute gem to find a new home. I\u2019ve treated this beauty like a member of the family\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every weekend, and kept in what I truly believe is showroom condition. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh, clean feel inside. Aside from maybe a microscopic pebble mark from a sunny afternoon cruise, she\u2019s practically perfect. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved with a capital L, this is the one. Come on over, let\u2019s grab a coffee, and I\u2019ll show you why this car is so special!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an echelon-tier specimen for the discerning enthusiast. This build features a blueprint-balanced powertrain with an aggressive cam profile and a port-matched intake manifold for optimized volumetric efficiency. The chassis has been bolstered with aircraft-grade billet aluminum subframe inserts to eliminate deflection, while the bespoke valving in the dampers provides unparalleled rebound control. Meticulously maintained with a focus on preventative maintenance, including recent timing chain tensioner calibration and a full cryogenic cleaning of the undercarriage. The paint boasts a mirror-finish depth thanks to a 10H ceramic coating over a flawless factory clear coat. This is a turn-key, track-capable masterpiece that demands zero compromises.",
      "price": 44850.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
